Wmns Gel Cumulus 23 'Aqua Angel'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Cumulus 23 ‘Aqua Angel’ applies a monochromatic pastel finish to the engineered mesh upper, made with at least 20% recycled content and featuring targeted zones of support and breathability. The lightweight build is mounted on two layers of FlyteFoam cushioning. 3D Space Construction is built into the top layer for enhanced compression with each stride, while ASICS’ Gel technology in the heel delivers superior shock absorption.

results.name: Wmns Gel Resolution 8 LE 'Earth Day'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Resolution 8 LE ‘Earth Day’ updates the performance tennis shoe with a sustainable build. 40% of the cream-hued mesh upper is made with recycled materials, including pre-owned garments and leftover fabric scraps, while the sockliner is produced with a solution dyeing process that reduces water usage and carbon emissions. The sneaker rides on a springy FlyteFoam midsole with Gel cushioning in the forefoot and heel.

Wmns Chuck Taylor All Star High 'Floral Print - Multi'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck Taylor All Star High ‘Floral Print’ delivers a lush take on the vintage canvas sneaker. Lined in breathable recycled mesh, the upper is entirely covered in a multicolor floral print that spans pink, green, lavender, coral and yellow hues. Standard Chuck Taylor elements remain intact, including contrast stitching, chrome eyelets and a circular All Star patch on the medial ankle. A white rubber midsole anchors the high-top silhouette.

results.name: Wmns Gel Cumulus 23 'Pink Salt'
results.story: The ASICS women’s Gel Cumulus 23 ‘Pink Salt’ showcases a one-note pastel finish on a plush running shoe named after fluffy cumulus clouds. 20% recycled materials are incorporated into the engineered mesh upper, featuring reflective accents for added visibility in low-light conditions. Responsive cushioning is provided by a dual-layer FlyteFoam midsole, equipped with 3D Space Construction for a smoother ride and visible Gel technology in the heel for superior shock absorption.

Wmns Chuck 70 High 'Embroidered Floral Print - Chambray Blue'
results.story: The Converse women’s Chuck 70 High ‘Embroidered Floral Print’ treats the classic silhouette to a summer-ready refresh. Organic canvas is utilized on the upper, finished in a subtle Chambray Blue color and covered in embroidered white and yellow blossoms. The high-top is mounted on a standard Chuck 70 midsole, featuring taller off-white rubber sidewalls in a glossy finish. Heritage details include a circular Chuck Taylor ankle patch and a vintage license plate affixed to the rear of the midsole.

Nike Dunk Low Green Glow (W)
results.story: The Nike women’s Dunk Low ‘Green Glow’ showcases traditional color blocking on a customary all-leather build. A crisp white base is contrasted by a vibrant shade of green on the sneaker’s eyestay, Swoosh, and forefoot and heel overlays. The verdant hue is repeated on the woven tongue tag and heel tab, both marked with standard Nike branding. The low-top rides on a two-tone rubber cupsole, equipped with a grippy outsole originally designed for pivoting on the hardwood.
